        </div>
        <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-black dark:text-pnw-sea-400">
          I'm an Analytics Engineering expert and Indie Music aficionado from Vancouver, Canada. 
          I build scalable data solutions and performant analytics teams.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-2 font-semibold text-black dark:text-pnw-sea-200">
          I can help you with:
        </p>
        <ul
          class="py-2 space-y-[3px] text-sm list-disc list-inside text-black dark:text-pnw-sea-400"
        >
          <li>Laying a scalable Data Analytics architecture</li>
          <li>Building a performant Data Science team</li>
          <li>Setting an AI-forward Data Democratization culture</li>
          <li>Managing KPI pipelines & dashboards</li>
          <li>and more...</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-6">
          <img src="/assets/images/tools/dbt.png" alt="dbt Labs" class="w-6 h-6" title="dbt Labs" />
          <img src="/assets/images/tools/snowflake.png" alt="Snowflake" class="w-6 h-6" title="Snowflake" />
          <img src="/assets/images/tools/bigquery.svg" alt="BigQuery" class="w-6 h-6" title="BigQuery" />
          <img src="/assets/images/tools/omni.png" alt="Omni Analytics" class="w-6 h-6" title="Omni Analytics" />
          <img src="/assets/images/tools/hex.png" alt="Hex" class="w-6 h-6" title="Hex" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="relative justify-end hidden w-full mt-10 md:flex md:pl-10 md:w-1/2 md:mt-0 md:translate-y-4 xl:translate-y-0"
      >
        <div class="relative z-50 w-full">
          
          <div class="relative z-30 px-10">
            <img
              src="/assets/images/photo.png"
              loading="eager"
              decoding="auto"
              class="relative z-30 w-full aspect-[790/1189] md:max-w-md mx-auto dark:-translate-y-0.5 rounded-3xl"
            />
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Separator text="Where I'm Working" />
  <CurrentWork />
  <div class="mb-14"></div>

  <Separator text="What I'm Building" compact />
  <Projects />
  <div class="mb-14"></div>

  <Separator text="What I'm Listening" />
  <SpotifyFeed />

  <Separator text="Where I'm Traveling" />
  <InstagramFeed />
  <div class="mb-14"></div>
